quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Na bene Aadi nabo barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,124,"Mugihe\tmwene\twabo\tHudu\t(iii)\tyababwira\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimuzotinya Imana yanyu"
  26,125,Ntankeka jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,126,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, kandi mungamburukire"
  26,127,"Kandi\tntaco\tnshaka\tkuri\tibi\tvyose,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri\tku muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,128,"Mbega mwiyubakira amazu ahari agatumba, uku n’ugufyinata muriko muragira"
  26,129,Mukiyubakira n’inzitiro nk’uko mubona yuko muzoramba mubuzima bwanyu bwose
  26,130,No mugihe muteye abandi mubatera n’ubwishime
  26,131,Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,132,Nimutinye uwabahaye ibi vyose muzi
  26,133,Ko ariwe yabahaye ibikoko hamwe n’ibibondo vy’abahungu
  26,134,Hamwe n’imirima n’amasoko y’amazi n’inzuzi
  26,135,Mu vy’ukuri ndabafitiye ubwoba bw’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka
  26,136,"Nabo bamwishuye bati:- n’ibisanzwe kuri twebwe\tkuko udushikirije ubwo butumwa canke ntube mubabu dushikiriza"
  26,137,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ingeso z’abantu baho hambere
  26,138,Natwe ntituzohanwa
  26,139,"Rero baramuhakana natwe duca tubibiza mumazi, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mu bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,140,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije